item.title: CVE-2020-2209|2024-08-04T07:01:41.258Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20testcomplete%20support%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins TestComplete support Plugin 2.4.1 and earlier stores a password unencrypted in job config.xml files on the Jenkins master where it can be viewed by users with Extended Read permission, or access to the master file system.
